let's talk about people

00:31:14.280 --> 00:31:15.860
that actually have rabies.

00:31:15.860 --> 00:31:16.810
Oh.

00:31:16.810 --> 00:31:20.700
Well, what if I gave them
rabies mixed with the bird flu?

00:31:20.700 --> 00:31:21.760
No.

00:31:21.760 --> 00:31:23.782
Well, I heard about
violent behavior

00:31:23.782 --> 00:31:25.990
from people that have been
infected with Lassa fever.

00:31:25.990 --> 00:31:26.990
What if I gave-- no.

00:31:30.250 --> 00:31:32.780
What if I modified
Marburg and combined it

00:31:32.780 --> 00:31:34.775
