of a rhinovirus

00:31:34.775 --> 00:31:37.090
and caused it become
completely airborne,

00:31:37.090 --> 00:31:39.260
and gave it the entire
population at once,

00:31:39.260 --> 00:31:41.640
and caused massive viral
amplification in anything

00:31:41.640 --> 00:31:45.010
