of the best moments.

00:31:50.320 --> 00:31:54.815
Was just having the doctor I was
talking to, go don't do that.

00:31:54.815 --> 00:31:56.891
Like that's a bad plan
that you have there.

00:31:56.891 --> 00:31:58.390
So that's how I got
my zombie virus.

00:31:58.390 --> 00:32:00.280
