00:35:54.055 --> 00:35:55.680
I'm just going to
laugh at you and then

00:35:55.680 --> 00:35:57.930
expect you to help me
when the comet is coming.

00:35:57.930 --> 00:36:00.570
So the first rule of a
good survival plan is

00:36:00.570 --> 00:36:03.120
don't tell anyone you're
not bringing with you,

00:36:03.120 --> 00:36:05.410
