full of breakable shit.

00:40:23.270 --> 00:40:24.960
Now, maybe your
five-year-old boy

00:40:24.960 --> 00:40:27.390
will become content just
balancing the bat on his hand

00:40:27.390 --> 00:40:28.860
and going whee.

00:40:28.860 --> 00:40:32.800
But most five-year-old boys
are going to start going, huh.

00:40:32.800 --> 00:40:33.800
OK.

