find both of the directions

01:01:55.940 --> 01:02:00.850
that they came from, for
which I am sad, so sad.

01:02:00.850 --> 01:02:05.380
People will sometimes hit on one
or the other, but never both.

01:02:05.380 --> 01:02:07.390
So sad.

