McGuire, which when I sign,

01:02:12.010 --> 01:02:15.950
is a great big M and a C and
a great big G and a squiggle.

01:02:15.950 --> 01:02:18.410
Mira Grant is just a great
big M, a dot, a great big G,

01:02:18.410 --> 01:02:19.560
and then a squiggle.

01:02:19.560 --> 01:02:22.070
